{"tid":232921,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好驚父母好快老？","createTime":"2017-05-07T07:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T08:08:25.000Z","uid":85205,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc898f8820c100c9b1075e1d70bffc5faf837b80","tid":232921,"uid":85205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T07:20:27.000Z","msg":"今日同阿媽係廳講野。佢同我講一諗起遲d我地幾姊妹出黎做野唔需要佢照顧就覺得宜家要盡量珍惜同我地一齊嘅日子。我聽到呢句就抬頭望下佢<br />\n突然先留意到阿媽唔知幾時開始，眼底多左幾條鄒紋，個樣老左好多。個下好心up<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我地個個都過18歲，唔洗佢好似以前咁照顧但係佢覺得我地仲係好細個好似以前咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前排病咗，阿媽即刻煲藥俾我"},{"pid":"4c6e1c658a52a2cb26ddccf2df3efaf0276a8c6a","tid":232921,"uid":89608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T07:21:40.000Z","msg":"生老病死, 人生必經, 睇化左冇乜野"},{"pid":"990d08d8a55615f331ae3c59ea47f09c41ce9e54","tid":232921,"uid":74271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T07:22:55.000Z","msg":"同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd64224277ae50b4db9e57f8f4b06091e8173f5","tid":232921,"uid":14482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T07:24:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8d6d81521d51ee1500e6e84a919173543d51342","tid":232921,"uid":109730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T07:27:18.000Z","msg":"驚 恭喜巴打有咁嘅覺悟 希望你會因為咁更加珍惜同兩老相處嘅時間 <br />\n我喺媽媽身體有事先識驚 宜家好撚後悔"},{"pid":"b10eadcbb5e7cceae1dd76dd52c4894af89b208e","tid":232921,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T07:28:47.000Z","msg":"無得驚"},{"pid":"112c9386b521589e25c5166f7c1afddf62036a94","tid":232921,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T07:29:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92d74c0a49265b76b929ba50c39febab6d03ab29","tid":232921,"uid":43765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T07:30:02.000Z","msg":"以前好驚 不過而家無感覺了